Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被人紧紧盯着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫福爷和兰芳对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是又失踪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 稍一松劲就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是又饿昏了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 清净了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家 不大对劲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 来探望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上校的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 抽烟的小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 赢了一局没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这游戏太没劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 半夜再出去切人就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少把霍克艾姐姐带来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我跟大姐说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得盯他到几时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「抱歉让你执行这么危险的任务」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「军务的事不必担心 算你病假」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但若被普通市民及除我们以外的军方人士发觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就有你好看的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有点鼓舞人心的消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交上女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚搬来这里诸事不便 多亏有她温柔待我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是极品好女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩了她应该很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 饿昏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 新国来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够远的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的签证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让路让路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕非法入境者了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿昏了 绝对饿昏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去军部露个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去修兹先生家打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想早点见到格蕾希娅阿姨和莉希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我们也马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹中校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来还有没有帮我们收集贤者之石的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟被大总统封了口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把我们得知的情报告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得中校应该在军法会议所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那间书库的钥匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 3号库是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用过之后都没收拾 乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我只是去拿需要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立即整理 请您稍候片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等下来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你先收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概10分钟左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开军事会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 算我多管闲事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还是别太勉强 好好休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是玛斯坦上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早安 弗卡上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 上校怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书库还开着门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是上校逼你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说上校在查什么呢 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情我也不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他问我有没有第五研究所相关的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 关于修兹准将的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多亏准将的介绍才能进来工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的工作也是堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好像瘦了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南部碰上点事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还见到艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去见达布利斯的师父 偶然碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹的死告诉他们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们迟早会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所和贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造石头的材料是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙本就爱管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是插手了艾尔利克兄弟的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了不该知道的事情 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若得知是自己的事把修兹卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致他的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两兄弟会伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也查到不少事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心隔墙有耳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 霍克艾中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然中尉在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月起我调来中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 今天怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来收集点情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便想跟修兹中校打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着老婆孩子 打算继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想见见他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别冲得太猛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这种时候把他们当小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他们还不必知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兄弟俩前进的阻力越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们迟早会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说阿姆斯特朗少校是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好人做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校不在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得告诉温莉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都去修兹先生家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚听说了修兹中校的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多话想对他说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也该和他告别一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没联系到你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 军方有好好送行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还挺周到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们可能听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他特别连升两级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是中校 是准将了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别连升两级？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下了还升职？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 中校怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹准将在爱德君出院后不久就被人杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人至今逍遥法外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我 是我连累了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹中校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一路小心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中央市来一定联系我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯穿着铠甲可没法吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们还没找到住处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人承担罪责就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是哥哥一个人的问题 是我们两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都决心要恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有人要为此牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那恢复身体又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话必须要跟格蕾希娅阿姨说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 温莉也来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公他知道了某些关于贤者之石的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人们杀死老公 是为了警告你们不要插手此事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于是我们把修兹先生卷进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了帮助别人而牺牲 还真像他的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前他就爱多管闲事 结果每次都吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想他一次都没后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要因此而放弃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们就此放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公的死就完全白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便贤者之石不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也还会有其他办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾希娅阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就按照自己认同的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你别哭呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂马上关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃饭身体撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后来自己试了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自吹自擂 做的还不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过跟格蕾希娅阿姨比差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候让修兹先生也尝尝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校在追查修兹的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是查出什么蛛丝马迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想把他放在眼皮底下监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把他调来中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能老实点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为珍贵的候补人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没从你男朋友那儿问出什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他是单纯还是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去收集情报试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦 格拉特尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 格拉特尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱扔垃圾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说拉丝特 只要让火焰上校老实点就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试试别的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么点子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱吠的狗只要给点吃的就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宪兵队司令部的亨利·道格拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们走一趟 枪也交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解释一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是马斯·修兹被害事件的嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后再听你解释
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉本人否定了罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集有关此人的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快 但要秘密进行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 帮我把这个花包一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 去约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个小帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了 索拉丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我也刚来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你 简
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我讲点有趣的故事吧
